videos.description: Andre Jones throws a bounce pass between defenders to Warith Alatishe, who rises up to smash down a two-handed dunk.

videos.description: Skylar Mays ties the game at 36-36 as he jumps the passing lane to get the steal and then stuffs a dunk on the other end.

videos.description: Javonte Smart misses a three, but Skylar Mays flies past the defense to get the tip-in at the basket.
